Package org.middleheaven.core.wiring Description

Wiring Toolbox This is and automated dependency injection engine. The engine is capable of resolving cyclic dependencies and can invoke by simple annotation of methods or constructors. The wiring toolbox does it best at not violating the encapsulation principle so direct access to fields although possible is discouraged.
